rgb(red, blue, green)
  - 0-255

#001122
  - red, blue, green represented as 2 hex characters 00 to FF 

hsl(hue, saturation, lightness)
  - hue 0-360
    - red : 0
    - green : 120 
    - blue : 240
  - saturation 0-100%
  - lightness 0-100%
  
linear-gradient(gradientDirection, color1, color2, ...) 
  - gradient direction is degrees, ex: 90deg
    - default 180 or top to bottom
  - color stops can be added as a percentage after the color to determine how much space it takes up 
    - linear-gradient(gradientDirection, color1 x%, color2 x%, ...) 

opacity 
  - 0 to 1.0 is 0 to 100%
  
alpha channel : sets opacity 
  - rgba(redValue, greenValue, blueValue, alphaValue);
    - alphaValue from 0 to 1.0
